- fontWeight >= 500 always
- Headings: purple[50] (#FAF5FF)
- Body: purple[200] (#E4CFFF)
- Caption: purple[300] (#D6B0FF)
- Gradient text: gradients.logoText (blue[400] → purple[600])
- CountUpNumber uses Czech locale formatting
